*Postaju* sve oprezniji kada se radi o novcu. (They are becoming more and more careful when it comes to money.) 

Ona *postaje* sve otvorenija prema drugima. (She is becoming more and more open to others.)

One *postaju* sve manje zainteresovane za politiku. (They are becoming less and less interested in politics.)

*Postaju* sve bogatiji zahvaljujući novom poslu. (They are becoming richer and richer thanks to their new job.) 

Oni *postaju* sve više i više zajedno. (They are becoming more and more together.)